<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/33930957.258410/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlu=
aW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTktMDItMjcvd2hvLWNhbi1zYXktd2hhdC1jYWxpZm9ybmlhLW1lYW5=
