; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-sty=
le: solid; background-color: #ccc;">via social media</a>=C2=A0that a Carta =
salesperson had contacted an angel investor in his company, telling them th=
at Carta had a "firm buy order" for the angel's shares in Linear.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">According to Saarinen, this angel investor is =
a family member who's never been publicly disclosed and who's "hardly onlin=
e."</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Moreover, Linear had never been asked to appro=
