<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In short, someone on Carta's "liquidity soluti=
ons" team had accessed Linear's confidential cap table data; leveraging the=
 core product as lead gen for a more lucrative effort. It was a massive eth=
ical breach, no matter how different lawyers might interpret Carta's privac=
y policy.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One VC told me it was akin to "Oracle using yo=
ur database to share supply-chain data or Salesforce using your CRM data to=
